@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 场景：地面站控制单架 UAV 的协议协作时序
hide footbox

actor "Ground Station" as GS
participant "UAV Runtime" as UAV #EEF2F4
participant "Flight Executor" as FC #F1F4F6

== Session ==
GS -> UAV : SessionHello
GS -> UAV : SessionAuthenticate
GS -> UAV : SessionCapabilities
GS -> UAV : SessionReady
UAV --> GS : Session 本地推进到 Active

== Authority ==
GS -> UAV : AuthorityRequest(action=Claim)\ntarget = Entity(UAV#1)
UAV --> GS : AuthorityStatus(state=Controller)\n或本地租约已生效

== Command ==
GS -> UAV : Command.Goto\nsession_id != 0\nttl_ms = motion window
UAV --> GS : CommandResult.Received
UAV --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted
UAV -> FC : 调度 Goto
FC --> UAV : progress / done
UAV --> GS : CommandResult.InProgress
UAV --> GS : CommandResult.Succeeded

== Uplink ==
UAV --> GS : StateSnapshot.VehicleCore
UAV --> GS : StateEvent.VehicleEvent (optional)

note right of GS
这是最小闭环：
Session -> Authority -> Command -> Uplink
缺任何一段，都不是完整控制路径。
end note
@enduml
